HEADWORD: Domino whist
<hw>Dom"i*no whist</hw>. <def>A game of cards in which the suits are
played in sequence, beginning with a 5 or 9, the player who gets rid of
his cards first being the winner.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

